name: Symmetrical A
description:
The art piece was inspired by the infamous ink blot cards used in psychiatry . Although not meant to test a viewer's mental conditions, this piece,  nevertheless, is capable of playing tricks with one's mind if gazed at for a long time. 

The convenience of this technique is in its algorithmic practicality: any element can be used to create an unlimited diversity of shapes and forms...

Thus, more of these will follow in due time.
